All of my works is free. If you'd like to support me, feel free to buy me a coffee. 👍

Recommend options

  • LoRA weight 0.7~1.0

  • Trigger words

    • base

    • Racing competition clothes :

      • navel, midriff, crop top, fingerless gloves, blue footwear, belt, open mouth, blue jacket, white pants, white gloves, sneakers, collarbone

      • (optional) : light trail, glowing eyes, electricity, glowing

    • Casual clothes :

      • collarbone, shirt, long sleeves, denim shorts, sneakers

    • Festival costume :

      • ponytail, hip vent, official alternate costume, sleeveless shirt, jewelry, black footwear, clothing cutout, black pants, black shirt, bridal gauntlets, baggy pants

    • Sailor costume :

      • sailor collar, neckerchief, pleated skirt, wide sleeves, black skirt, belt, collarbone, long sleeves, grey thighhighs, blue shirt, loafers

    • Aged down version :

      • kindergarten uniform, school hat, bag, white socks, bandaid on knee, black shorts, blue shirt, long sleeves, aged down, yellow headwear, white footwear, ears through headwear

      • (optional) drooling

Use animefull based model

  • Settings

    • DPM++ Series(SDE Karras, 2M Karras, etc.)

    • about 20 steps, CFG scale 3.5~6.5

    • kl-f8-anime2.vae

    • CLIP skip = 1

    • If using highres

      • Latent series

      • Denoising strength 0.50~0.65

LoRA training info

  • based on Animefull-pruned

  • 163 images of tamamo cross

    • 4x low quality 45 images

    • 8x medium quality 62 images

    • 16x high quality 56 images

    • => 1 epoch = 1572 images

  • replaced character feature tags with tamamo cross \(umamusume\)

    • horse girl, horse tail, grey hair, blue eyes, etc.

  • using aspect ratio bucketing

  • resolution : 768x768

  • rank=alpha=16

  • using dadaptation

  • batch size = 4, 8 epochs trained

  • clip skip = 1

This LoRA may be compatible with animefull-based models (ex. AbyssOrangeMix Series...)

All uploaded images are generated by AOM3A1
